{"tid":1755188,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"下一盤大棋，將軍抽車，染黃","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:10:38.000Z","uid":78383,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff883e9db1207e366f602fe913e605fabaec662","tid":1755188,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"區議會既勝利，其實就係政府比我地將左一次軍，但係絕對未將死，我地而家要抽車。<br />\n<br />\n車，就係藍絲。睇番票數，黃藍比係6:4。40%既藍絲係政府最後既資產，換句說話講，如果黃藍比去到73，基本上我地必勝。<br />\n<br />\n區議會勝利其實帶比我地最好既文宣平台。根據心理學理論Illusory truth effect，如果一個人長期曝露於一種資訊之中，佢既信念係會動搖既。換言之，我地要長期做好文宣，利用好區議會平台，對長者好D，減少圍爐打飛機。<br />\n<br />\n最後想講，文宣人人都有責，日常生活當中可以嘗試將長輩染黃。因為主流民意已經顯示左黃係多數，你地講既野係佢地眼中係會合理左。我相信將呢40%既藍絲染黃不是夢。"},{"pid":"1bd07f9bcb68dbcf3075bb38e2b4c4aa8d8190c5","tid":1755188,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6a982519ffdb40e860144404cb9d584cf3f993","tid":1755188,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d261442cbe4bc2100621afebad0a5d4ae07862","tid":1755188,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"365998cd98ccffc8d8d36f9ceb61e89a18919b9e","tid":1755188,"uid":87735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:08:50.000Z","msg":"今屆各區議會應該集中協助發展黃色經濟圈<br />\n咁樣成個民主發展先唔會失去持久力"},{"pid":"a15be0b2ad6263daf6ffb1c26eb549d6fd91765d","tid":1755188,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7ad721f0afdc9fa548bc700344d43bad9ac64c","tid":1755188,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"